**Terminal B (beyond §XX).** (a) Scope: coderived not derived; Malcev obstruction. (b) Primary: Positselski 2011 Mem AMS 212 associative + BD 2004 §§3.3-3.4 + EZ 1985 + Chenevier 2014. (c) Universal trace $\hbar^2 K=-1$ requires B.

